<br>
The elemental forms are not meant to be damage  aa but more so utility aa. I think a great fix for elemental form aa would be the following.<br>
<br>
Elemental Fire Form : the 3rd point spent extends the time used to 72mins so that it can be refreshed as soon as it wears off. Also it gives Improved Damage 3 while in the form.<br>
<br>
Elemental Earth Form : the 3rd point spent extends the time used to 72mins so that it can be refreshed as soon as it wears off. Also it gives regent conservation 3 (seeing as how most would use this on a raid for the extra hps and modding. Regent conservation would be a good idea).<br>
<br>
Elemental Water Form :  the 3rd point spent extends the time used to 72mins so that it can be refreshed as soon as it wears off.  Gives mana preservation 3 (also bump the mana regen up by 2 points)<br>
<br>
Elemental Air Form : the 3rd point spent extends the time used to 72mins so that it can be refreshed as soon as it wears off.  Gives spell haste and extended enhancement 3.<br>
<br>
Adding these simple affects to the elemental forms would make mages work to get them all because there would be times they would all come in handy. As of now there is only one that has any real use and the rest are crap at best.<br>
<br>
